  <h2>Tag Searching</h2>
  <p>As of <a href="../../communities/using/deploy-communities.md#latestfeaturepack">feature pack 1</a> (FP1), tag searching is performed using <a href="../../sites/developing/using/framework.md#tagcharacteristics">tag titles</a>.</p> 
  <p>Prior to FP1, search was performed using <a href="../../sites/developing/using/framework.md#tagid">tag ids</a>.</p> 
